label chapter15:
    scene room with fade

    "Three days."
    "I don't go to the academy."
    "I sit in my room."
    "Minji texts me constantly."
    "I read them and don't reply."

    minji "In-Ha."
    minji "Please just tell me if you're alive."

    "I type: I'm alive."
    "I don't send it."

    "On the fourth day.."
    "Someone knocks."
    "Not Minji's knock."
    "Slower."

    inha "Who is it?"

    yejun "It's me."

    inha "How do you know where I live."

    yejun "Minji told me."
    yejun "She was worried."

    inha "I'm fine."

    yejun "I know."
    yejun "I brought food."
    yejun "You don't have to open the door."
    yejun "I'll leave it here."

    thought "..."
    thought "He remembered I like tangerines."
    thought "I told him that once."
    thought "Years ago."

